    "PRIVACY_S1_BODY": "We collect information you provide directly (name, phone, email) and information generated by your use of the platform (listings, favourites, search history, device information).",
    "PRIVACY_S2_TITLE": "2. How We Use Your Information",
    "PRIVACY_S2_BODY": "We use your information to provide and improve our services, send notifications about your listings and saved searches, and communicate with you about your account.",
    "PRIVACY_S3_TITLE": "3. Information Sharing",
    "PRIVACY_S3_BODY": "We do not sell your personal information. Contact details you provide on listings (phone, WhatsApp) are visible to other users as part of the listing.",
    "PRIVACY_S4_TITLE": "4. Data Retention",
    "PRIVACY_S4_BODY": "We retain your account data while your account is active. You may request deletion of your account and associated data at any time by contacting us.",
    "PRIVACY_S5_TITLE": "5. Contact",
    "PRIVACY_S5_BODY": "For privacy-related questions or requests, please contact us through the Contact Us page."
