  "HELP": {
    "TITLE": "Help Center",
    "SUBTITLE": "Find answers to common questions about using Barmha.",
    "Q1": "How do I post a listing?",
    "A1": "Tap the 'Post' button in the top navigation bar. Choose your listing category, fill in the details across the three steps (info, price & location, photos), then submit. Your listing will be live immediately.",
    "Q2": "How do I edit or delete my listing?",
    "A2": "Go to My Account → My Listings. Each listing has Edit and Delete buttons. You can also deactivate a listing temporarily using the pause button — it won't appear in search results but can be reactivated later.",
    "Q3": "How do I save a listing to my favourites?",
    "A3": "Tap the heart icon on any listing card or detail page. Favourited listings are saved to My Account → Favourites. You'll receive a notification if the price of a favourited listing changes.",
    "Q4": "How do I contact a seller?",
    "A4": "On any listing detail page, you'll find options to call the seller, send a WhatsApp message, or send an in-app message. Phone numbers are hidden by default on cards — tap the call icon to reveal.",
    "Q5": "What is a Saved Search?",
    "A5": "When browsing listings with filters applied, tap the bookmark icon in the header to save that search. Saved searches appear in My Account → Saved Searches. You can set up notifications to be alerted when new listings match your saved filters.",
    "Q6": "How do I change the language?",
    "A6": "Use the language toggle button (ع / EN) in the top toolbar or at the bottom of the side menu to switch between Arabic and English.",
    "Q7": "How do I report a listing?",
    "A7": "Open the listing detail page, scroll down and tap the Report button. Choose the reason and submit. Our team will review the report promptly.",
    "Q8": "How do I delete my account?",
    "A8": "Contact us through the Contact Us page and request account deletion. We will process your request and permanently delete your account and all associated data within 7 business days."
